    howToCatch: ['Cast spinners or spoons near river mouths in fall (Aug–Nov)', 'Troll hoochies or herring near surface (15–30 ft) in salt water', 'Work tidal flats and river estuaries at high tide', 'Coho are aggressive biters — flashy lures work well'],
  },
  steelhead: {
